data.description: Don't pass up this unique opportunity to house hack in a single family home! Located just minutes away from the mall and a variety of restaurants, this spacious tri-level home boasts four cozy bedrooms along with kitchen and living areas that are perfect for gatherings. A hidden gem awaits on the lower level, featuring a private entrance and the potential for rental income or use as a mother-in-law suite. Complete with its own kitchenette and bathroom, these separate living quarters provide independence and convenience. This is a perfect opportunity to house hack in a great neighborhood on a quiet dead end street. The lower unit is currently renting for $850 per month.
